{"tid":1648771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完今日情況，聽日18區改主要7-8區會唔會實際啲？","createTime":"2019-10-12T10:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T14:31:34.000Z","uid":33577,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"582e21078166d8bdd85b1816d65c214284d8229a","tid":1648771,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"而家睇可能18區每區只係集結到200-300人<br />\n但如果集中幾區效果可以強好多<br />\n我唔想再灰<br />\n想大家道氣可以延續落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想死咗嘅手足係Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集中幾區嘅話<br />\n新東：大埔 沙田<br />\n新西：元朗 屯門 荃灣<br />\n九東：觀塘<br />\n九西：旺角<br />\n港島：銅鑼灣 <br />\n<br />\n18區做後備方案<br />\n俾狗圍先至由18區和理非圍魏救趙<br />\n有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n趁而家仲有十幾個鐘<br />\n大家可唔可以一齊集思廣益下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284d1d00b927d70a9047734b194db0c648e4c2c4","tid":1648771,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eded8106d8f7644305b3b9daca10d90095729d2","tid":1648771,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e1476d3c47da15a87e2258d3bea1f1ac6c0657","tid":1648771,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8919dba70a56df59b4427012f61e255e9f98d303","tid":1648771,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"同上星期一樣好啲，太散驚危險，太集中又易圍捕<img src=\"